# Tutorial for using docker with r
In this tutorial, base data is read from an Azure container, it is then filtered and written back to the container.
The code is run in Docker.

## Installation Instructions

1. Install docker
2. Add sudo to your docker group
3. Clone this repo to your machine
4. Build the image 'docker image build . -t <name of new image>'
5. Run a docker container from the image ' docker run -it -v "$(pwd):/usr/src/orders" <name of new image> 

